videos.description: John Fulkerson goes up-and-under on LSU's Duop Reath, making him leave his feet for the layup.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Fulkerson makes nice move for bucket

videos.description: The Volunteers make  four passes at the top of the key before Admiral Schofield drains the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Tennessee's unselfish play leads to 3-pointer

videos.description: Randy Onwuasor strips Volunteers' Admiral Schofield then takes it coast-to-coast for the and-1 basket.
videos.headline: Onwuasor's feisty defense leads to LSU bucket

videos.description: Jordan Bowden makes a nice lead pass for Derrick Walker and he throws down a nasty jam.
videos.headline: Volunteers' Walkers throws down rim-rattling dunk

videos.description: Lamonte Turner makes a nice crossover and then pulls up for the nice jumper.
videos.headline: Volunteers' Turner shows off smooth handles
